The following input helpers needs to be created, they enable you to input the necessary settings in the lovelace UI for the calculator to do its work:
Take note that it's extremely inportant that the names and values are exactly correct with spaces and everything since 
I use conditional card with conditions based on these values.

type: input_number
name: pizzacalculator_number_of_pizza
lowest value: 0
highest value: optional
step length: 1
unit of measurment: optional

type: input_number
name: pizzacalculator_doughweight
lowest value: 0
highest value: optional
step length: 5
unit of measurment: optional

type: input_number
name: pizzacalculator_water
lowest value: 0
highest value: 100
step length: 1
unit of measurment: optional

type: input_number
name: pizzacalculator_flour
note: (should always be set to 100)
lowest value: 99,9
highest value: 100
step length: 0,001
unit of measurment: optional

type: input_number
name: pizzacalculator_salt
lowest value: 0
highest value: 4
step length: 0,1
unit of measurment: optional

